snippet.title: Johnny Depp Breaks Down In Tears After People Still Believe in Amber (VIDEO)
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp is retaliating with tears as he reacts to individuals actually trusting in Amber Heard. The video, which was taken as of late, sees Johnny separating on camera as he responds to individuals accepting that Amber was attacked by him. Johnny's hand starts shaking as he understands general society is as yet blaming him for every one of the things that occurred among him and Amber. "She was at a party the following day," Johnny says in dismay as tears stream down his face. "With her sister and every one of her companions, as nothing occurred." The video additionally sees Johnny inquiring as to whether what he is saying is valid or not, instead of accepting all that they read via online media.
